{
  "id": "63177f7489561900217c36ed",
  "title": "置かれた場所で咲きなさい",
  "created": 1662484345,
  "updated": 1674371087,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63177f7489561900217c36ed",
      "text": "置かれた場所で咲きなさい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484345,
      "updated": 1662484351
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec8aff09e00004223d7",
      "text": "日本語で「置かれた場所で咲きなさい」というと置いた主体が誰なのか不明瞭。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370761,
      "updated": 1674370762
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec9aff09e00004223d9",
      "text": "元々の詩では明確に「神様があなたを植えたところで咲け」と言っている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370762,
      "updated": 1674370762
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec9aff09e00004223da",
      "text": "\t著者は神学者の[ラインホルド・ニーバー - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%83%9B%E3%83%AB%E3%83%89%E3%83%BB%E3%83%8B%E3%83%BC%E3%83%90%E3%83%BC]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370762,
      "updated": 1674370762
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec9aff09e00004223db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370762,
      "updated": 1674370762
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdeebaff09e0000c3f018",
      "text": "この言葉を「新卒で入社した会社に不満があっても、その会社で活動しなさい」などの意味で使う人がいるが、間違いだと思う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370795,
      "updated": 1674370853
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec9aff09e00004223df",
      "text": "\t原文では[\" 神様はあなたを特別な場所に植えてくださいました。あなたがそれを知れば、他の人と分かち合うことで、あなたの個性は輝きます。その \"輝き \"を私たちは \"花 \"と呼んでいます。]と書いている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370762,
      "updated": 1674370984
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec9aff09e00004223e3",
      "text": "\tつまり、この「場所」とは「あなただけの特別なもの」を指している。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370762,
      "updated": 1674370896
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdf57aff09e00004223e8",
      "text": "\t\t決して「たまたま新卒で入社した会社」という意味ではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370904,
      "updated": 1674370904
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdf7caff09e00004223ec",
      "text": "\tそれを知れば、花が咲く、と言っている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370941,
      "updated": 1674370963
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdf93aff09e00004223ed",
      "text": "\t\t日本的な言葉で言うなら「[天命を知る]」が近い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370963,
      "updated": 1674371062
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdf65aff09e00004223e9",
      "text": "\t\t現代的な言い方に言い換えるなら「あなたはあなたらしく咲きなさい」が近いと思う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370917,
      "updated": 1674371087
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec9aff09e00004223e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370762,
      "updated": 1674370902
    },
    {
      "id": "63ccdec8aff09e00004223d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674370761,
      "updated": 1674370761
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f7faff09e00000841c2",
      "text": "この言葉の出典",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484351,
      "updated": 1662484370
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f92aff09e00000841c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484371,
      "updated": 1662484371
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f93aff09e00000841c5",
      "text": "\"Bloom where God has planted you.\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484371,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841c6",
      "text": "Please bloom where God has placed you.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841c7",
      "text": "Rather than give up, make the best of your life and bloom like a flower.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841c8",
      "text": "To bloom is to live happily.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841c9",
      "text": "Let your joy make others happy.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841ca",
      "text": "Your smile is contagious.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841cb",
      "text": "When you are happy and show it by your smile",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841cc",
      "text": "Others will know it and are happy too.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841cd",
      "text": "God has planted you in a special place.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841ce",
      "text": "If you know it share it with others, your personality will shine.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841cf",
      "text": "It is that \"shine\" which we call \"Bloom\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841d0",
      "text": "When I bloom in the place where God has placed me",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841d1",
      "text": "My life becomes a beautiful flower in the garden of life.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f9faff09e00000841d2",
      "text": "Bloom where God has planted you.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa0aff09e00000841d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484388
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa0aff09e00000841d4",
      "text": "\"神があなたを植えた場所で咲いてください\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484388,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841d5",
      "text": "神があなたを置かれた場所で咲いてください。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841d6",
      "text": "あきらめるのではなく、自分の人生を最大限に生かし、花のように咲いてください。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841d7",
      "text": "咲くということは、幸せに生きるということです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841d8",
      "text": "あなたの喜びで人を喜ばせてください。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841d9",
      "text": "あなたの笑顔は伝染します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841da",
      "text": "あなたが幸せで、それを笑顔で示せば、他の人もそれを知って幸せになります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1674371025
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841dc",
      "text": "神様はあなたを特別な場所に植えてくださいました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841dd",
      "text": "あなたがそれを知れば、他の人と分かち合うことで、あなたの個性は輝きます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841de",
      "text": "その \"輝き \"を私たちは \"花 \"と呼んでいます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841df",
      "text": "神様が置いてくださった場所で私が咲くとき",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841e0",
      "text": "私の人生は、人生の庭に咲く美しい花となる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177fa9aff09e00000841e1",
      "text": "神があなたを植えた場所で咲きなさい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484396,
      "updated": 1662484396
    },
    {
      "id": "63177f84aff09e00000841c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1662484356,
      "updated": 1662484356
    }
  ]
}